title: Bonus Episode: National Fraternity League
description:
Domonique is joined by Andscape's senior writer David Dennis Jr. to talk about a former NFL player venturing into politics. Then, Andscape's culture host and producer Sheila Matthews joins the show to talk drama in the music world.
